data.name: 0000 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: In the end, we wound up with with quite the unbalanced lineup once again, huh…

data.name: 0001 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Well, I can't deny that this group won't have trouble preventing Haruhi's rampage.

data.name: 0002 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: So? What are we going to do from here on out?

data.name: 0003 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: That's obvious! An on-scene investigation!

data.name: 0004 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Madam Brigade Chief was in a good humor, with an exuberant smile plastered on her face.

data.name: 0005 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I don't know what she thinks is so worth getting excited about…

data.name: 0007 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: And by that, you mean class 1-9, I presume?

data.name: 0008 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Right! Thinking about it logically, assuming class 10 exists, it'd have to be next to class 9.

data.name: 0009 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Three people create the wisdom of Manjushri, so four must mean hyper Manjushri wisdom!

data.name: 0010 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Our scene is just over there. Let's go!

data.name: 0011 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Haruhi lumbered over like a yeti striding through the snow.

data.name: 0012 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I'm begging you, don't find anything that'll cause me trouble…

data.name: 0015 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Nagato, is it okay for her to go near the site?

data.name: 0016 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: If she finds the aforementioned impossible classroom, it'll cause quite a ruckus.

data.name: 0017 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: There is a chance of discovery.

data.name: 0018 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: However, I will conceal it to the limit of my ability.

data.name: 0019 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Sorry it's always like this, but you're the only one I can rely on.

data.name: 0020 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Understood.

data.name: 0021 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Kyon! And Yuki! What are you doing?! Hurry up and get over here you two!

data.name: 0022 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Yes, yes, heading over straight away, of course. Good grief…

data.name: 0024 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I don't think there's anything I need to clarify. We're outside class 1-9…

data.name: 0025 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: In other words, the danger zone of the sudden appearance of that class 1-10.

data.name: 0026 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Hmm, the plate still says class 9.

data.name: 0027 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Naturally. Because such a thing as "class 10" doesn't exist.

data.name: 0028 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: It exists, I'm sure of it.

data.name: 0029 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: We came here to find it, so hurry up and look around.

data.name: 0030 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: We've been tasked to investigate without any sort of how-to guide.

data.name: 0031 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Yuki, don't you feel some kind of mysterious power? Like, the spiritual kind?

data.name: 0032 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Haruhi, why is it that you're operating under the assumption that Nagato…

data.name: 0033 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …can even sense that kind of occult energy?

data.name: 0034 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: For some reason, it seems like she can, doesn't it?

data.name: 0035 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: You wouldn't be wrong to be frightened by the fact that she's not entirely incorrect.

data.name: 0037 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: …Nothing particular.

data.name: 0038 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Really? Not even some kind of uncanny presence?

data.name: 0039 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Nothing.

data.name: 0040 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Could it just be the Computer Society's mistake after all? With it being so dark…

data.name: 0041 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: That might be the case, but we can't say for sure.

data.name: 0042 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Besides, it's the iron rule of the SOS Brigade to expect the more exciting option!

data.name: 0043 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Another needless rule. Although I'm sure the one who thought it up will forget soon anyways.

data.name: 0044 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: The word of the computer club is unreliable. We should look for another eyewitness.

data.name: 0045 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Then we can get out of this troublesome place, which would do me a big favor.

data.name: 0046 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: If you mean a new testimony, Mikuru's already getting that ready for us right now.

data.name: 0047 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: …Huh? Wait a second.

data.name: 0048 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What is it? Did you notice another mysterious presence or something?

data.name: 0049 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Not that. Mikuru. Right now she's alone in the computer club, you know.

data.name: 0050 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Indeed, that's the duty she was assigned.

data.name: 0051 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: All alone, with the Computer Society…

data.name: 0052 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: I'm a little… worried.

data.name: 0053 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What are you worried about?

data.name: 0054 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: You know how cute Mikuru is? She's gone off to that room full of boys, you know?

data.name: 0055 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: I wouldn't consider that much of a reason to be worried about it.

data.name: 0056 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Let me remind you that Asahina is a resp- ected upperclassman in the year above us.

data.name: 0057 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Well, no, she's actually a lovely time traveler whose age is unclear.

data.name: 0058 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Worst-case scenario, it would be a massive issue! All thanks to my careless supervision!

data.name: 0059 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Worst-case… happening to Asahina…? That's too absurd—as if that could ever happen.

data.name: 0060 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: But hold on, there's certainly something about Haruhi's point I simply can't ignore.

data.name: 0061 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Even I can tell as much—Asahina's extreme cuteness is an objective truth.

data.name: 0062 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: If those Computer Society boys flock around her… if by any chance that comes to pass…

data.name: 0063 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: ...we'll have an instant brawl. The whole SOS Brigade will end up in one big war party.

data.name: 0064 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: The computer club is in the old building, so it's quite far.

data.name: 0065 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: If we are to go there, it would be best to hurry.

data.name: 0066 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I see. This is our excuse to get Haruhi away from the scene…

data.name: 0067 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Let's go. I'm worried about Asahina.

data.name: 0068 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: That's not what you were saying before.

data.name: 0069 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: I've reconsidered. The computer society is solely made up of boys, after all.

data.name: 0070 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: It's probably nothing, but I can imagine them wanting to spite us.

data.name: 0071 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Whether it's spite or not, I definitely think they hold a grudge.

data.name: 0072 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: We stole a brand-new PC from them after all.

data.name: 0073 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Everyone, let's hurry over to the Computer Society!

data.name: 0074 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Either way, I'm grateful for the chance to leave this place.

data.name: 0075 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Asahina, I'm on my way, so I beg that nothing happens to you…

data.name: 0078 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: With speed that would even turn a cheetah pale, we returned to the old building.

data.name: 0079 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: And when we revisited the Computer Society's clubroom…

data.name: 0080 (377.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: #SK0 *Sniffle*… Fuueeh…

data.name: 0081 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Wha-?!

data.name: 0082 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The first thing I saw was, undoubtedly, Asahina's tears.

data.name: 0083 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: A-Asahina?!

data.name: 0084 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: The hell!? Computer Society!! What did you do to Mikuru?!

data.name: 0085 (377.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: Sniff… Uff… Ah… Kyon… Suzumiya…

data.name: 0086 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Whoever's responsible for this, show yourself! The president!

data.name: 0087 (377.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: Wh-what's going on? You guys again?

data.name: 0088 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What on earth do you call this?! I'll act violent if you don't give a good answer!

data.name: 0089 (377.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: Huh? What are you ta-…

data.name: 0090 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Tell us what happened here. Why is Asahina crying--

data.name: 0091 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Who cares why?! Mikuru's crying, you know?!

data.name: 0092 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: They'll have to be sentenced to death! The most severe of the most severe punishments!

data.name: 0093 (377.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: U-uh… Ummm…

data.name: 0094 (377.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: What are you guys talking about with all this inexplicable nonsense?

data.name: 0095 (377.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: We have nothing to do with the fact she's crying…

data.name: 0096 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: So you did do something?! Right?! I can't let you get away with that!

data.name: 0097 (377.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: Wha… H-hey… #SK0I can't breathe--

data.name: 0098 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Haruhi continued to press the president, tightening up his tie.

data.name: 0099 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Nice, Haruhi! For once I'll support you with full force!

data.name: 0100 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Go ahead and confess. What kind of sick act have you been trying to pull?

data.name: 0101 (377.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: #SK0N#sk-nothing… #SK0Ekkk

data.name: 0102 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Then, in that very instant--

data.name: 0103 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Suddenly, an annoying electronic sound. It sounds like energy draining… What is it?

data.name: 0104 (377.ja) CLUB_MEM_A (部員Ａ)
data.value: P-p-p-president?! The power source… The power source has…!

data.name: 0105 (377.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: All the PCs… They all shut down at once…

data.name: 0106 (377.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: Agh. W-what did you say…?

data.name: 0108 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Miss Suzumiya, it's rather difficult to say this, but…

data.name: 0109 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Please, take a look by your feet.

data.name: 0110 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: My feet? Hmm? What is it?

data.name: 0111 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Rolling by Haruhi's feet was a disconnected plug.

data.name: 0112 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Seems like Miss Suzumiya's feet caught on it, causing the power to drop…

data.name: 0115 (377.ja) CLUB_MEM_A (部員Ａ)
data.value: N-no way! The data is all gone!

data.name: 0116 (377.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Here as well. Everything's blank!

data.name: 0117 (377.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: Th-that… That can't be…

data.name: 0118 (377.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: U-um… Kyon…

data.name: 0119 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Asahina, are you ok?! Haruhi's handling the Computer Society's punishment.

data.name: 0120 (377.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: I'm crying because, um… I tripped in the hallway over there.

data.name: 0121 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Huh?

data.name: 0122 (377.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: So, um… The Computer Society people didn't do anything wrong…

data.name: 0123 (377.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: I fell and hit the tip of my nose, so it really hurt…

data.name: 0124 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: So, the Computer Society are innocent?

data.name: 0125 (377.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: Yeah…

data.name: 0126 (377.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: W-we said so didn't we?! That we didn't do anything!

data.name: 0127 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Ahh… Oh, well… Sorry.

data.name: 0128 (377.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: So what are you going to do about all our lost data?!

data.name: 0129 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Well that's… How do I put it? It's Haruhi's personal blunder, so…

data.name: 0130 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Well, it was totally misleading.

data.name: 0131 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: I truly believed you'd attacked Mikuru, so naturally I went into a frenzy.

data.name: 0132 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: If I just put the plug back in, it's fine, right? Here.

data.name: 0133 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: You could hear the whirring of electronics as the computers started up… as if they just restarted.

data.name: 0134 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Lost data won't recover.

data.name: 0135 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Well, active computers were suddenly shut down after all…

data.name: 0136 (377.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: #SK0Aaaaahhhhhhhhhhh…

data.name: 0137 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The club president and his members were all dumbfounded staring at the restarting PCs.

data.name: 0138 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: …I understand how you feel, Computer Society.

data.name: 0141 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Looks like we wasted our time. Also, shouting made me thirsty.

data.name: 0142 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Let's head back to the clubroom at once. Come on, Mikuru.

data.name: 0143 (377.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: Hwuh? O-okay… But…

data.name: 0144 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Just come back to the clubroom, and make tea when you're there.

data.name: 0145 (377.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: O-okayyy.

data.name: 0147 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Seems like the Computer Society plans to leave it at that. You're a demon, Haruhi.

data.name: 0148 (377.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: The data is… Our data is…

data.name: 0149 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Didn't Taniguchi or Kunikida say that before? "Don't get involved with Haruhi Suzumiya"?

data.name: 0150 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Sorry, Computer Society. Just think of it as bad luck and accept it.

data.name: 0152 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: The people of the Computer Society were considerably dispirited, weren't they.

data.name: 0153 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: It'd be weird if they weren't.

data.name: 0154 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: So, where's the culprit, Haruhi, gone?

data.name: 0155 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Clubroom. Entered with Mikuru Asahina.

data.name: 0156 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Pretty carefree of her, leaving without a word of an apology…

data.name: 0157 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: I suppose it's best we left them with an apology.

data.name: 0158 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Even at the best of times, our history with them leaves them no choice but to hold a grudge.

data.name: 0159 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: What do you think? Should I go do it?

data.name: 0160 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Otherwise, you have the option of asking Nagato.

data.name: 0162 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Making Nagato go by herself would be cruel, so I'll go apologize myself.

data.name: 0163 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: However, if it's a girl, they won't get as angry, don't you think?

data.name: 0164 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Huh, good point…

data.name: 0165 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Don't worry.

data.name: 0166 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Hmm…

data.name: 0167 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I don't think it would look good, as a man, if I sent Nagato by herself…

data.name: 0168 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: What should I do?

data.name: 0169 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Sorry Koizumi, but I'm gonna leave it to you.

data.name: 0170 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Understood. Then wait here for a moment. I'll be right back.

data.name: 0171 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: I can't wait in the clubroom?

data.name: 0172 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Indeed, I actually have an idea, and it requires the two of you to help…

data.name: 0173 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Got it.

data.name: 0174 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Well then, I'll see you momentarily.

data.name: 0175 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Koizumi dashingly reenters the Computer Society clubroom.

data.name: 0176 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: …Is he gonna be okay?

data.name: 0179 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Then, after a little while…

data.name: 0180 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Sorry for making you wait.

data.name: 0181 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: That was quick. You're already done?

data.name: 0182 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Indeed. I left them with a humble apology.

data.name: 0183 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: They were still completely dumbfounded, with hollow expressions on their faces, but…

data.name: 0184 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: They'd completely accepted it and nodded back at me.

data.name: 0185 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: How should I put it… A deeply pitiful Computer Society.

data.name: 0186 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …Nagato, can I leave it to you?

data.name: 0187 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: You can.

data.name: 0188 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: I'll go apologize.

data.name: 0189 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Nah, I'm gonna do it. I'm not gonna make you go in there by yourself.

data.name: 0190 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: If you don't mind, I just want you to be with me, that's all.

data.name: 0191 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Understood.

data.name: 0192 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: I'm by your side.

data.name: 0193 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Sorry.

data.name: 0194 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Koizumi, you head back to the clubroom and keep Haruhi company.

data.name: 0195 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Actually, I'll be waiting here.

data.name: 0196 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: I've got something I want to put into action, and I need the two of you to help.

data.name: 0197 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Something to put into action? What is it?

data.name: 0198 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: I'll explain later.

data.name: 0199 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: He gave the usual fishy smile, seeming to suggest something.

data.name: 0200 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Alright. We'll be back as soon as possible.

data.name: 0201 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Of course. I'll be waiting.

data.name: 0202 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Let's go, Nagato.

data.name: 0204 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: With that said and done, Nagato and I reentered the Computer Society clubroom…

data.name: 0205 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: It was only a few minutes. Before we knew it we had left again.

data.name: 0207 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: How was it?

data.name: 0208 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Uh… How should I put it? It was like apologising to an empty husk.

data.name: 0209 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: The Computer Society accepted our apology.

data.name: 0210 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: You say accepted, but it felt more like they just nodded with their souls still yet to return.

data.name: 0211 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Well, we more or less got the idea across. I suppose that'll probably do.

data.name: 0212 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Nagato lightly bowed her along with me when we apologized. Sorry, Nagato.

data.name: 0213 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: So, you said you wanted our help with something or another. What is it?

data.name: 0214 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Indeed. I'll explain, but we should go somewhere else.

data.name: 0215 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Koizumi glanced at the SOS Brigade clubroom. So it's about Haruhi, huh?

data.name: 0216 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Let's head to the third floor of the main building.

data.name: 0217 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The third floor of the main building? You want to go back to class 1-9?

data.name: 0218 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: We might be able to trick Miss Suzumiya.

data.name: 0219 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Trick Haruhi…?

data.name: 0220 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: I'll explain as we go. Let's hurry before Miss Suzumiya catches on.

data.name: 0224 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Koizumi's explanation was incredibly simple. The trick of a fraud.

data.name: 0225 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: You want us to tamper with the class plates, offsetting everything from 1-6 to 1-9…?

data.name: 0226 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: That's right. Class 7's plate where 6's should be, class 8's in place of class 7's.

data.name: 0227 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …What about the remaining class 9?

data.name: 0228 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: That's the point. Where class 9's plate was, will be no plate, number, or anything.

data.name: 0229 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: In other words, class 1-10.

data.name: 0230 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: That's such a simple trick, isn't it? Surely Haruhi would catch on?

data.name: 0231 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: She probably would. In fact, I'm doing this under the assumption that she would notice.

data.name: 0232 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …What do you mean?

data.name: 0233 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Think of it like this. It'll look like someone's prank.

data.name: 0234 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: So what?

data.name: 0235 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Don't you understand?

data.name: 0236 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: I don't understand. Also, it doesn't feel good being tested.

data.name: 0237 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: I'm sorry about that. What I'm trying to say is simply this.

data.name: 0238 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: The Computer Society fell for such a prank…

data.name: 0239 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: In other words, it was all just a fake.

data.name: 0240 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …I see.

data.name: 0241 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Someone set up the prank, and the Computer Society fell for the prank…

data.name: 0242 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: It would mean that both parties have fabricated the non-existent classroom.

data.name: 0243 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: You've really thought this through. For sure, Haruhi would probably accept that explanation.

data.name: 0244 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: And probably get angry. I hope she doesn't direct it all at the comptuer society again.

data.name: 0245 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Got it. What do you want us to do?

data.name: 0246 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Let's take down these plates, then. Do you mind starting from class 6?

data.name: 0247 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: I'll start from class 9.

data.name: 0248 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What about Nagato? Surely she won't be able to reach?

data.name: 0249 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Height won't be a problem.

data.name: 0250 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: I can do it like this.

data.name: 0251 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: …Saying so, Nagato raised both her hands towards the class 6 plate. What's she planning?

data.name: 0252 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …Nagato, what are you doing?

data.name: 0253 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Destroying the plate.

data.name: 0254 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Huh?

data.name: 0255 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Performing a dismantling process has no requirement for direct contact.

data.name: 0256 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Whoa whoa whoa, wait a second!

data.name: 0257 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: We're not destroying them, just taking them down!

data.name: 0259 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Class 6's plate will be unnecessary.

data.name: 0260 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Well, I suppose if we're offsetting them, you're not wrong, but…

data.name: 0261 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: We'll have to put it back later, so don't break it. Just taking it off will be fine.

data.name: 0262 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Understood. I'll take it.

data.name: 0263 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: If you could, that'd be great. Oh, you can use my back as a stool.

data.name: 0264 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I squat down and lend my back and shoulders to Nagato as a stool.

data.name: 0266 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Nagato's lightweight body put a moderate amount of pressure on my back.

data.name: 0267 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: As you are.

data.name: 0268 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Yeah, got it.

data.name: 0269 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Then, in that moment…

data.name: 0270 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: My phone dared to ring in a time like this.

data.name: 0271 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Answering the phone in this posture is a little tricky, but…

data.name: 0272 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Uh, hello?

data.name: 0273 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Oi! What are you doing slacking off?!

data.name: 0274 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Oh it's Haruhi… Guh. What is it?

data.name: 0275 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: As if you don't know! After all this time, you still haven't come back to the clubroom!

data.name: 0276 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Ah, we ended up busy with various things, like patching things up with the Computer Society.

data.name: 0277 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Even though Mikuru made delicious tea especially…

data.name: 0278 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: It's gone completely cold already!

data.name: 0279 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Damn it, that's really unfortunate.

data.name: 0280 (377.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Anyway, start heading back this very second! I'll give you 3 minutes! I'm counting!

data.name: 0281 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: We can maybe barely make it if we run as fast as we can… Don't be unreasonable, Haruhi.

data.name: 0283 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: What happened?

data.name: 0284 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: A call from Haruhi. Return to the clubroom at once, she says.

data.name: 0285 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: At once?

data.name: 0286 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Were you finished taking those down?

data.name: 0287 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: No, I was just about to.

data.name: 0288 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Nagato, is the class 6 plate off?

data.name: 0289 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: I can remove it at any moment.

data.name: 0290 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: It seems I spent too long explaining… What should we do?

data.name: 0291 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: If we just hang around, Haruhi will probably come and find us.

data.name: 0292 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Oh right, for the time being…

data.name: 0293 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Let's just take off the class 6 plate.

data.name: 0294 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Understood.

data.name: 0295 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Though, I don't think it will mean anything if we just take off the class 6 plate…

data.name: 0296 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Maybe we can use it for something later.

data.name: 0297 (377.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: We should at least be able to use it as evidence of foul play.

data.name: 0298 (377.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: It's off.

data.name: 0299 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Nice, good job. I'll look after that.

data.name: 0300 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Let's head back to the clubroom before Haruhi starts looking for us.

data.name: 0301 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: That's a shame. I thought it was a good idea…

data.name: 0302 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: You're right. We might still have a chance, but for now, it's a tactical retreat.

data.name: 0303 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: If Haruhi came out and found us like this, that would be even worse.

data.name: 0304 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Putting this plan on hold for now and returning to the clubroom is our best move.

data.name: 0305 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: What a shame. If we only have 10 minutes more, we could've achieved our goal…

data.name: 0306 (377.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Let's think of another move. For now, we'll hurry back.

data.name: 0307 (377.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Nothing we can do about it, I suppose.

data.name: 0308 (377.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Entrust Koizumi with it

data.name: 0309 (377.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Rely on Nagato

data.name: 0310 (377.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: At least take class 6

data.name: 0311 (377.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Give up and head back to the clubroom
